Add the environment to the ALR_info.yml
Follow the standard PLv3 onboarding process
Once the environment is created by TFE, the SPN called <env>-ALR-ADO-SERVICE-CONNECTION-SPN will be created as well. Ensure the SPN belongs to the HRB-AZURE-<env>-READER security group. You might need to create a BMC ticket to have the group assigned if you can't assign the AAD group by yourself.
Create the service connection in ADO based on the SPN mentioned above
